name: PartnerRole
description: Represents a role in the partner relationship.
summary:
The {PartnerRole} object in the {salesforce} application represents a partner role with the following attributes:
- Id (data type: id)
- MasterLabel (data type: string)
- ApiName (data type: string)
- SortOrder (data type: int)
- ReverseRole (data type: picklist)
- CreatedById (data type: reference)
- CreatedDate (data type: datetime)
- LastModifiedById (data type: reference)
- LastModifiedDate (data type: datetime)
- SystemModstamp (data type: datetime)
label: Partner Role Value
